data.description: Charming and immaculately kept home in the sought after Royse City ISD! Soak in the sunshine in the huge backyard with family and friends or simply unwind and relax after a hectic work day in the spacious front porch. This 4 bed 2 bath home features high ceilings, upscale granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in kitchen. A great living and dining open concept layout! Laminate flooring through most common areas and easy to clean tile flooring in bathrooms! Master bedroom offers large windows for lots of natural light overlooking the grand backyard and ensuite master bath gives you a stand up shower along with his and hers sink and a generous size walk in closet! Within walking proximity to community park, trails and pool! Easy access to HWY I-30 and a short commute to all the amenities downtown Royse City has to offer and to Lake Ray Hubbard in Rockwall! Don't miss out on owning your dream home!! This property won't last long! Make your move now!!
